These are the actions a player can take via http API:

/ListGames
(Shows games that are joinable)

/CreateGame
(a button that creates a game)

/JoinGame/<GameID>
(Join a game based on url, perhaps take over a bot mid game?)

/StartGame/<GameID>
(Start the game from the lobby)

/Bet/<Value>/<GameID>
(Bet when asked)

/PlayCard/<Value>/<GameID>
(Play a card from their hand to lay down)

Other actions, such as shuffeling and updating will take place backend via Lambda
